    public class Command
extends java.lang.Object

    The Class Chat Command. Commands to communicate between clients and chat server. Used serialization for transfer command object on network.

        public Command()

      • Command

        public Command(java.lang.String commandString)
        Instantiating a new command, parsed from the input commandString. Command parsed:
      • CommandName.CMDMSG
      • CommandName.CMDENTER
      • CommandName.CMDEXIT
      • CommandName.CMDPRVMSG

        If the message is empty or the command is not found the list, return CommandName.CMDERR command.

Parameters:
commandString - the command string
